title: Sicwitit Sticwitit Wes P Productions, LLC Will Release Scoreboard, a Song Honoring You and I of the Working Class on Labor Day
text:
Sicwitit Sticwitit Wes P Productions, LLC Will Release Scoreboard, a Song Honoring You and I of the Working Class on Labor Day
Sicwitit Sticwitit Wes P Productions, LLC will release the fifth single from I Am That, I Am: For The People, By The People, Scoreboard on 9-7-15.
Phoenix, AZ, September 07, 2015 --( PR.com )-- Wes P continues to respond to his critics merging into the music industry with Scoreboard climbing the charts honoring the working class on Labor Day.
"Change is our only guarantee and I am the guarantor." As an avid free thinker, he is bringing a new spectrum of thought to light and turning the current realm. As his largest influence, Tupac Shakur said he wouldn't change the world but he'd spark the mind that does. Wes P's mind is set to change the world and make a difference.
In order to request this incredible new single contact your local radio station and ask for it to be placed into rotation or visit www.iamwesp.com/
The release of Scoreboard embarks on the climb to the top of billboard charts for Wes P's I Am That, I Am: For The People, By The People.
